---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Thanks for subscribing | Sky Lavelle"
  description="You have joined The Project Recovery Brief."
  noindex
>
  <section class="section min-h-[60vh] flex items-center">
    <div class="container max-w-2xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-emerald-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-3">You are on the list.</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-warm-700">
          The first issue of The Project Recovery Brief will land in your inbox shortly. In the meantime, there is useful material below.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <a href="/articles" class="group flex flex-col p-5 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-white hover:border-ochre-400 transition-colors">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-warm-900 group-hover:text-ochre-600 mb-2">Read the articles</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-warm-700 leading-relaxed flex-1">Practical guides on project recovery, business cases, procurement and steering committee reporting.</p>
          <span class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-ochre-600">Browse articles &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://lavelleptyltd.com.au/templates" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group flex flex-col p-5 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-white hover:border-ochre-400 transition-colors">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-warm-900 group-hover:text-ochre-600 mb-2">PMO templates</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-warm-700 leading-relaxed flex-1">Structured template packs for project recovery, business cases, procurement and steering committee reporting. Available through Lavelle Pty Ltd.</p>
          <span class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-ochre-600">View at Lavelle Pty Ltd &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://lavelleptyltd.com.au/free-tools" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group flex flex-col p-5 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-white hover:border-ochre-400 transition-colors">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-warm-900 group-hover:text-ochre-600 mb-2">Free PMO tools</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-warm-700 leading-relaxed flex-1">Free checklists and tools for project recovery, business case readiness, procurement evaluation and steering committee reporting.</p>
          <span class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-ochre-600">View at Lavelle Pty Ltd &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="group flex flex-col p-5 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-warm-100 hover:bg-warm-200 transition-colors">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-warm-900 group-hover:text-ochre-600 mb-2">Need advisory support?</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-warm-800 leading-relaxed flex-1">If you are working through a difficult delivery situation, an enquiry is a sensible starting point.</p>
          <span class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-ochre-600">Send an enquiry &rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
